Communicated by:
ProMED-mail
<promed@promedmail.org>

[The previous outbreak of Newcastle disease (NCD) was reported on 28 Dec 2016 in the province of Vidin, see summary at http://www.oie.int/wahis_2/public/wahid.php/Reviewreport/Review/viewsummary?reportid=22103

In 2013, NCD was also reported in Kardzali's province. See event summary and map http://www.oie.int/wahis_2/public/wahid.php/Reviewreport/Review/viewsummary?reportid=12924. - Mod.CRD

A HealthMap/ProMED-mail map can be accessed at: https://promedmail.org/promed-post?place=5294077,63090.]
